<section xml:id="numbers-everyone" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Everyone Can Reason Quantitatively</title>

  <!-- All content before subsections goes inside <introduction> -->
  <introduction>
    <p>
      Here is an unordered list of special characters and content tags:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>special characters: &amp;, &gt;, and &lt;</li>
      <li><em>emphasized text</em></li>
      <li><q>quoted text</q></li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Here is an ordered list of items:
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>apple</li>
      <li>pine</li>
      <li>pineapple</li>
    </ol>

    <p>
      Let's start with some inline math expressions: <m>e = mc^2</m>. Followed by math expressions in its own standalone structure:
      <md>A = \pi r^2</md>
    </p>

    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse non ultrices enim. Aenean sodales ligula efficitur purus pharetra imperdiet. Nullam libero leo, rhoncus ac nulla vitae, euismod tempus augue.
